      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winna Schkehpã Kahte\nbiſa ka weena Reestawa/ un win-\nna Schkehpã Afminis biſa no\nfechtimts Sihketem Dſelſes/ un\ntas preeſchturramu Bruunau-\nNeffeis gabje winna Prechtchã.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schis nu stahweja / un\nfanze us Israëta Pulkeem / un\ntazzija us teem: Rapehz gribbat\njuhs iſeet Karrã taifitees? Neg-\ngi es efmu weens Willsteris / un\njuhs effat Saula Kalpi/ tsmekle-\njeet no juuns weenu/ kas pee man\nletja nahk.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ja tas warrehs ar man\nkautees/ un manni nokaus / tad\ngribbam mehs jums par Kalpeem\nbuht/ bet ja es winnu pahrwar-\nru/ un winnu kanju / tad buh-\nfeet juhs nuuns par Kalpeem /\nun kalpoſeet mums.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wehl fazzija tas Wiliste-\nrıs: Es efmu ſchodeen tohs Isra-\netã Pulkus apkannojts : Dohdeet\nman weenn Wihru/ ka mehs koh-\npã kanjamess.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rad nu Sauls un wiss\nIsraëts ſchohs Wahrdus ta Wi-\nlistera dsirdeja/ tstruhzinajahs tee\nun bihjajahs tohtt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Dahwids nu/ kas weens\nDehſs biſa ta Eewrätitſka Wihra\nno Betlemes Inhda / Jsajus\nWahrdã/ tam biſa uſtoni Dehli/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jsaja trihs wezzaße\nDehſi nogahje Karrã Saulau-\npakat / un winna treijo Dehſa\nWahrdĩ/ kas Karrã gabje/ bija\nElijahs tas pirndsimmis / un\nwinna ohtrajs Abinadabs / un\ntas treschajs Sammus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Dahwids bija tas ma-\nsakajs/ un tee trihs leelakee bija\nSaulam pakat gahjuſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Dahwids gabje/ un\natgreesehs no Saula/ jawã Teh-\nwa Awis gamniht eekſch Bet-\nlemes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tas Wilisteris igah-\nje Rihtõs un Wakkarõs/ un rah-\ndijahstur tychetrdefinitis Deenas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Jsajus us fa-\nwu Dehlu Dahwidu : Nemmi\njelle preeſch taweem Brahteem\nweenu Eepu no ſchahm ſwillina-\ntahm Wahrpahn/ un ſchahs def-\nmits Maites / un tezz Lehgert\npee taweem Brahteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet ſchohs definitis See-\nrus noneſe tain Ahwerſtam / un\npeeinekle tarus Brahtus / ka-\nteem klaſjahs/ un nemum weenu\nSihtni no teem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Sauls/ un tee/ un-\nwiffi Israëta Wihri bija Obsoliu\nEleiſa ar teem Wilistereem kar-\nrodami.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad zeblehß Dahwids\nagri/ un pamette tuhs Awis pre\nfa Ganna/ un nezebme ( tahs\nLeetas) un nogahje / ka Jsajus\n"
    }
